Title: Javac 4-valve manifold kit (R410A)
Description: Built to EN 973 T3, this Javac four valve manifold with continental hoses is hardwearing and easy to use with 80mm gauge heads and all manifolds either dual seal piston valves or quarter-turn mechanical valves. Title: Testo 557s smart set with wireless temperature probes, wireless vacuum probe
Description: This Testo 557s smart vacuum kit includes a smart digital manifold with four-way valve block as well as wireless vacuum and clamp temperature probes. Making carrying out measurements on refrigeration, air conditioning systems and heat pumps simple and quick, this kit has a large graphical display along with stored programs to guide the user and enable automatic determination of vital parameters, including superheat, pressure drop test and evacuation. Easily connected, Bluetooth probes for temperature, pressure and humidity provide additional flexibility of use while compatibility with the Testo app allows the engineer to take care of digital documentation on-site. Highly durable, this kit works reliably in even tough conditions.
